body_html: Right now, we don't have TensorFlow-specific profiling tools available, but a sampling profiler (such as pprof) should give enough information to point you in the right direction.

body: Right now, we don't have TensorFlow-specific profiling tools available, but a sampling profiler (such as [`pprof`](http://goog-perftools.sourceforge.net/doc/cpu_profiler.html)) should give enough information to point you in the right direction.
